{
  "stem": "26142.15",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But this soldier, he was able to get somehow a little boat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that boy, one of the Jewish boys-- his name was Ganz-- they got together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they, by boat, crossed over the-- the Vistula River.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they-- they surrendered to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Next morning when we were getting to become-- we-- we were terribly scared that the guy-- we didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That-- here was a Jewish boy missing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he one-- one of the-- of the-- of the soldiers missing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But next day, the Russians, through loudspeakers, announce to us, yesterday two of your people came over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We warn you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You should surrender.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You should come over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "If not, you are going to have the same.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then, you know, they would start shooting and cursing in Russian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they would also play Hungarian-- Hungarian melodies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You could hear it across with loud speakers. that's how close we were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were day, we were loaded up-- brought in, and loaded up to the-- on the trains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We heard that in this city there were some Jews working in a factory, but we couldn't-- we couldn't-- we couldn't get in touch with them whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I think if you-- if you heard of I think that was one of the factories that was in that-- in that city that he-- he was there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We heard about it when we were there, that there are some people that are- are still working here, Jewish people in a factory.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They loaded us up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And it was very, very strange that all this time we were never-- never accommodated with-- with transportation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We had to carry everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We had to walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But that time, they were-- we had four [NON-ENGLISH], four groups.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
